<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>cz-cli Benchmark Report — {{ run_id }}</title>
<style>
  body { font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif; margin: 2rem; color: #222; }
  h1 { font-size: 1.4rem; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: 4px; }
  table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  th, td { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 6px 10px; text-align: left; }
  th { background: #f5f5f5; }
  .faster { background: #d4edda; }
  .slower { background: #f8d7da; }
  .bar-wrap { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
  .bar { height: 14px; background: #4a90d9; border-radius: 2px; }
  .bar.agent { background: #e07b39; }
  .score-high { color: #28a745; font-weight: bold; }
  .score-low  { color: #dc3545; font-weight: bold; }
  .meta { color: #666; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>cz-cli Benchmark: Direct Commands vs Agent Run</h1>
<p class="meta">Run ID: {{ run_id }} &nbsp;|&nbsp; Cases: {{ total_cases }} &nbsp;|&nbsp; Runs per case: {{ runs_per_case }}</p>

<h2>1. 总览对比（中位执行时间）</h2>
<table>
  <tr>
    <th>用例</th><th>类型</th>
    <th>直接命令 (ms)</th><th>Agent Run (ms)</th>
    <th>时间比 (agent/direct)</th>
    <th>工具调用次数 (direct / agent)</th>
  </tr>
  {% for row in summary_rows %}
  <tr>
    <td>{{ row.case_id }}</td>
    <td>{{ row.case_type }}</td>
    <td class="faster">{{ row.direct_ms }}</td>
    <td class="slower">{{ row.agent_ms }}</td>
    <td>{{ row.ratio }}x</td>
    <td>{{ row.direct_tools }} / {{ row.agent_tools }}</td>
  </tr>
  {% endfor %}
</table>

<h2>2. 工具调用链时间轴</h2>
{% for row in timeline_rows %}
<div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem">
  <strong>{{ row.case_id }}</strong>
  <div style="margin-top:6px">
    <span style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#555">直接命令</span>
    <div class="bar-wrap">
      <div class="bar" style="width:{{ row.direct_bar_px }}px"></div>
      <span style="font-size:0.8rem">{{ row.direct_ms }}ms &nbsp; [{{ row.direct_seq }}]</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:4px">
    <span style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#555">Agent Run</span>
    <div class="bar-wrap">
      <div class="bar agent" style="width:{{ row.agent_bar_px }}px"></div>
      <span style="font-size:0.8rem">{{ row.agent_ms }}ms &nbsp; [{{ row.agent_seq }}]</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
{% endfor %}

<h2>3. 上下文传递得分（多轮场景）</h2>
{% if context_rows %}
<table>
  <tr><th>用例</th><th>步骤</th><th>直接命令得分</th><th>Agent Run 得分</th><th>预期关键值</th><th>直接命令命中</th><th>Agent Run 命中</th></tr>
  {% for row in context_rows %}
  <tr>
    <td>{{ row.case_id }}</td>
    <td>Step {{ row.step }}</td>
    <td class="{{ 'score-high' if row.direct_score >= 0.8 else 'score-low' }}">{{ "%.0f"|format(row.direct_score * 100) }}%</td>
    <td class="{{ 'score-high' if row.agent_score >= 0.8 else 'score-low' }}">{{ "%.0f"|format(row.agent_score * 100) }}%</td>
    <td>{{ row.expected }}</td>
    <td>{{ row.direct_found | join(", ") }}</td>
    <td>{{ row.agent_found | join(", ") }}</td>
  </tr>
  {% endfor %}
</table>
{% else %}
<p>无多轮场景数据。</p>
{% endif %}

</body>
</html>
